Exploration enrichment pathways with differentially expressed (DE) genes between old versus young

Team Le Grand

17 dcembre,2021

Pathway explored : REACTOME REGULATION OF INSULIN LIKE GROWTH FACTOR IGF TRANSPORT AND UPTAKE BY INSULIN LIKE GROWTH FACTOR BINDING PROTEINS IGFBPS

This pathway contain 142 genes.

In these 142 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes in the enrichment.

D4_sCs
16
